  "response": "Jon Acuff left the Dave Ramsey company in 2013 after working there for three years as a blogger and part of the marketing team. The exact reason for his departure was not publicly disclosed, but Acuff mentioned that it was a personal decision and he wanted to focus on his own writing and speaking career. There were no public indications of any conflicts or negative reasons for his exit. Since leaving, Acuff has gone on to write several successful books and continue his career as a motivational speaker.",
